        public boolean isHelpAvailable()
        Tells whether or not the help is available.

        Returns:
        true if the help is available, false otherwise

      • enableHelpKey

        public static void enableHelpKey(Component component,
                                 String id)
        Enables the help for the given component using the given help page ID.

        The help page is shown when the help keyboard shortcut (F1) is pressed, while the component is focused.

        Parameters:
        component - the component that will have a help page assigned
        id - the ID of the help page
